{
  "id": "RAW_a962c2",
  "title": "字节跳动大规模推荐模型训练系统 Primus 亮相系统顶会 ATC 2025",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MzYzMjE0MQ==&mid=2247515125&idx=1&sn=76327a826884cdf27378a0159ab10726",
  "date": "2025-07-10 03:16:00",
  "author": "字节跳动技术团队",
  "siteName": "字节跳动技术团队",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><br></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fe172629&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F5EcwYhllQOjXp47iaGZticfHr3iaChpNEgB38n0glzqicjyXFkticexibFbyaJUvmddeGH6oHxIvsiaY4JwHLJiaibe5rQg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 36px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 1.5;color: rgb(0, 91, 183);transition: color 0.35s;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;font-size: 24px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(236, 236, 236);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">🔥 简介:深度推荐模型统一训练系统Primus</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">搜索、广告、推荐是互联网业务的重要组成部分。在模型日益庞大、用户基数不断增长的背景下，如何高效完成数万亿样本的训练，已成为业界公认的技术挑战。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\">字节跳动基础架构-基础技术-训练设施团队联合AML-Engine团队，与浙江大学、上海交通大学合作，并在搜索、广告、推荐等团队的大力支持</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\">下</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，设计并开发了</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\">一个面向大规模深度学习推荐模型（Deep Learning Recommendation Model, DLRM）的全自研统一训练系统Primus</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，相关成果已被计算机系统领域顶级会议 USENIX ATC录用 ，标志着 Primus 在工业界落地和学术界影响上的双重认可。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\">论文标题</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：Primus: Unified Training System for Large-Scale Deep Learning Recommendation Models</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\">论文作者</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：Jixi Shan, Xiuqi Huang, Yang Guo, Hongyue Mao, Ho-Pang Hsu, Hang Cheng, Can Wang, Jun Song, Rui Shi, Xiaofeng Gao, Jingwei Xu, Shiru Ren, Jiaxiao Zheng, Hua Huang, Lele Yu, Peng Xu, Guihai Chen</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\">论文地址</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：<a href=\"https://www.usenix.org/conference/atc25/presentation/shan-jixi\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.usenix.org/conference/atc25/presentation/shan-jixi</a></span></p>\n  <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;height: 1px;overflow: visible;width: 633.812px;margin-top: 32px;margin-bottom: 32px;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(61, 168, 245), rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3), rgb(61, 168, 245));border-width: 0px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n  <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 36px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 1.5;color: rgb(0, 91, 183);transition: color 0.35s;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;font-size: 24px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(236, 236, 236);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">📌 背景:大规模 DLRM 训练的三重困境</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">如图所示，过去5年，随着字节跳动内部推荐业务的迅猛发展，单个DLRM的日均训练数据量从最初的 20TB 快速增长到 160TB，CPU虚拟核心数使用总量也从 150 万核扩充到 900 万核，涉及的 GPU 使用量更是达到数万张。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100031462\" data-ratio=\"0.9771428571428571\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" style=\"width:317px;height:310px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9d18f180&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5EcwYhllQOjqgKsriaujLibQg41iapGdU61pZaq9qYlz6dEcddWG67UsgDIwCzEgE0EGjqgMHUBTgnJHicicD8hicpeA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">图：过去 5 年 DLRM 训练规模增长趋势</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">现有的训练系统面临三大痛点：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 28px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0px;list-style: inherit;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\">资源调度割裂：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-weight: normal;\">大规模部署通常跨越由不同调度系统管理的异构资源池，弹性训练策略缺乏跨环境操作的能力，限制了资源的高效利用。</span></span></strong></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0px;list-style: inherit;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\">数据编排复杂：</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-weight: normal;\">海量样本分散在各种存储系统中且具有多样化的格式，读取与预处理多源批式和流式数据容易形成瓶颈。</span></span></strong></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0px;list-style: inherit;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\">模型时效性不足：</span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">用户行为和偏好的不断演变，单一的离线、在线、或先离线后在线的训练模式难以平衡“长期记忆”与“实时适应”。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;height: 1px;overflow: visible;width: 633.812px;margin-top: 32px;margin-bottom: 32px;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(61, 168, 245), rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3), rgb(61, 168, 245));border-width: 0px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n  <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 36px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 1.5;color: rgb(0, 91, 183);transition: color 0.35s;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;font-size: 24px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(236, 236, 236);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">🚀 创新:统一的资源调度/数据编排/训练范式</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">Primus 针对上述三大痛点，提出了以</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\">统一资源调度、统一数据编排、统一训练范式</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">为设计核心的训练系统架构。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100031469\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3148148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c6e5b648&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5EcwYhllQOjqgKsriaujLibQg41iapGdU61yJKPmv9lh9YbHoE03A9KljmgDkcfic9lO5fTgDV6wWpMT5OLJOhFLsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">图：Primus系统整体框架</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 20px;line-height: 1.5;color: rgb(0, 91, 183);padding-left: 6px;transition: color 0.35s;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🌟 01 | 统一资源调度</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100031470\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.18981481481481483\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c2308d28&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5EcwYhllQOjqgKsriaujLibQg41iapGdU61Wka28cXUibvVB8o7Eic8aCfm3MEv1ibNEVbGqeWfvvKiaCNcgMuHYoKIOg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">图：Primus系统跨环境多策略资源调度</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">Primus 通过统一资源控制器和动态扩缩容管理器进行资源整合。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">统一资源控制器引入统一资源抽象技术，即用户资源定义（Custom Resource Definitions, CRD）标准化 DLRM 训练作业和异构资源，提供跨调度系统如YARN和Kubernetes的统一API，在多集群资源间实现多策略动态扩缩容。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">动态扩缩容管理器根据实时指标选择合适策略，水平扩缩支持在大规模集群场景下实现动态并行，自动调整数据执行器与训练执行器的比例，垂直扩缩支持调整单个执行器的 CPU 和内存资源，提高资源利用率。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 20px;line-height: 1.5;color: rgb(0, 91, 183);padding-left: 6px;transition: color 0.35s;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🌟</span></span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">02 | 统一数据编排</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100031471\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.25462962962962965\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c5dac04d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5EcwYhllQOjqgKsriaujLibQg41iapGdU61v2KHVcetrBN5sUrXL8OfkHVJzUtibwxHeoT4rziaIylDVHhK5jJMH0Hw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">图：Primus系统多源批流数据编排</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">Primus 通过抽象数据定义和获取逻辑，优化数据编排速度。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">Primus 提出统一的三层数据定义，包括数据集、数据流和数据源层，有效管理 DLRM 的训练数据集。通过这一定义，进一步设计了数据任务图生成（Data Task Graph Generation, DTGG）机制以进行数据编排，提高多源批式和流式数据的处理效率，适应训练作业的多样化数据需求。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据任务图生成（DTGG）技术包含 Timer 、Data Source、Joiner和Sink四类算子，数据驱动器通过DTGG快速按时间顺序跨数据源生成数据任务，并由数据执行器运行任务提供数据，洗牌机制也做了优化以更好解决数据处理的瓶颈。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 20px;line-height: 1.5;color: rgb(0, 91, 183);padding-left: 6px;transition: color 0.35s;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🌟 03 | 统一训练范式</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100031472\" data-ratio=\"0.18703703703703703\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fc67a4ce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5EcwYhllQOjqgKsriaujLibQg41iapGdU61OuRa4iakJmicFDmFRSRrnOjD2nqYKkotKtKFia39APeR0kcVxmLXar6UQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">图：Primus系统在离线混合训练范式</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">Primus 提供混合训练推荐模型框架（Mixture Training Recommendation Model, MTRM），系统性支持记忆塔（Memory Tower） + 适应塔（Adapt Tower）的双塔结构，通过不同的计算图控制批式数据和流式数据的学习顺序，对两个塔分别进行参数更新，从而既保持对历史分布的记忆，又能快速适应新趋势。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时，也引入了混合数据优先级机制，使用缓冲区长度和重要性计算并提供行级优先级控制，避免流式数据激增无法及时处理导致的模型效果下降。</span></p>\n  <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;height: 1px;overflow: visible;width: 633.812px;margin-top: 32px;margin-bottom: 32px;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(61, 168, 245), rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3), rgb(61, 168, 245));border-width: 0px;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-